             was indicted for <rs id="t18290115-251-off1347" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290115-251-off1347" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290115-251-off1347" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290115-251-cd1348" type="crimeDate">8th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-251-off1347 t18290115-251-cd1348"></join>, 1 jacket, value 30s.; 1 pair of trouseres, value 15s.; 1 waistcoat, value 10s., and 1 shirt, value 8s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18290115-251-victim1913" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Downie
                  <interp inst="t18290115-251-victim1913" type="surname" value="Downie"></interp>
